## Modifications Implemented To Improve Model Functionality (ME Class)**



**a.) Dynamically Scalable Max Pooling:**  This module replaces static max pooling operations ("MAXPOOL")with dynamically scalable ones based on attention mechanisms between feature maps (“Attention-Guided MAX POOL”). This enhances learning capabilities while preserving spatial information from larger inputs.<br>   




 **b ) Multiscale Feature Fusion**: Instead relying solely upon one convolutional layer after "Maxwell" operation,this implementation introduces additional layers at different scales allowing finer grain features extracted earlier be combined effectively later.**





   







